{100}{}{Dr. Henry}
{200}{}{You see Dr. Henry, the resident Medical Researcher.}
{210}{}{You see a pudgy looking man with a shiny bald head, and thick-lensed glasses.}
{210}{}{This guy is so out of place it's painful. He's got that egghead, not living in the real world air about him, that's for sure.}
